\c 18
\s Lokho okunikwa abapristi lamaLevi
\p
\v 1 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuAroni: Wena lamadodana akho lendlu kayihlo kanye lawe\x + 17.13.\x* lizathwala ububi bendlu engcwele; futhi wena lamadodana akho kanye lawe lizathwala ububi bobupristi benu\x + 18.23. Eks. 28.38.\x*.
\v 2 Labafowenu, isizwe sakoLevi, isizwe sikayihlo, basondeze-ke lawe ukuze bahlanganiswe lawe\x + Gen. 29.34.\x*, bakusize\x + 3.7.\x*. Kodwa wena lamadodana akho kanye lawe lizakuba phambi kwethente lobufakazi\x + 3.10.\x*.
\v 3 Bazagcina umlayo wakho, lemfanelo zethente lonke\x + 3.25,31,36.\x*; kodwa kabayikusondela ezitsheni zendlu engcwele lelathini\x + 16.40.\x*, ukuze bangafi, labo lani\x + 4.15.\x*.
\v 4 Bazahlanganiswa lawe, bagcine imfanelo zethente lenhlangano kuyo yonke inkonzo yethente; kodwa owemzini kayikusondela kini\x + 17.13.\x*.
\v 5 Njalo lizagcina imfanelo zendlu engcwele lemfanelo zelathi\x + 3.38.\x*, ukuze kungabi kusaba khona ulaka phezu kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + 16.46. Levi 10.6.\x*.
\v 6 Mina-ke, khangelani, ngithethe abafowenu amaLevi bevela phakathi kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + 3.12,45.\x*. Bayisipho kini, baphiwe iN\nd kosi\nd* ukwenza inkonzo yethente lenhlangano\x + 3.9; 8.19.\x*.
\v 7 Ngakho wena lamadodana akho kanye lawe lizagcina ubupristi benu kuzo zonke izinto zelathi\x + 3.10.\x* laphakathi kweveyili, likhonze\x + Heb. 9.3,6.\x*. Nginike ubupristi benu bube ngumsebenzi wesipho; kodwa owemzini osondelayo uzabulawa.
\p
\v 8 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuAroni: Mina-ke, khangela, ngikunike ukuphathwa kweminikelo yami yokuphakanyiswa yazo zonke izinto ezingcwele zabantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + Levi 7.32.\x*; ngiziphe wena, ngenxa yokugcotshwa, lamadodana akho\x + Eks. 29.29. Eks. 40.13,15.\x*, ngesimiso esilaphakade\x + 18.11,19,23; 19.10,21; Levi 3.17.\x*.
\v 9 Lokhu kuzakuba ngokwakho okuvela ezintweni ezingcwelengcwele, zivela emlilweni\x + Eks. 40.10.\x*; yonke iminikelo yabo, yonke iminikelo yabo yokudla\x + Levi 2.2,3; 10.12,13.\x*, layo yonke iminikelo yabo yesono\x + Levi 4.22,24; 6.25,26.\x*, layo yonke iminikelo yabo yecala, abazayibuyisela kimi\x + Levi 7.7; 14.13.\x*; izakuba ngengcwelengcwele ibe ngeyakho leyamadodana akho\x + Eks. 40.10.\x*.
\v 10 Lizakudlela engcweleni yezingcwele; wonke owesilisa uzakudla; kuzakuba ngcwele kuwe\x + Levi 6.16,18,26,29; 7.6.\x*.
\v 11 Lalokhu ngokwakho: Umnikelo wokuphakanyiswa wesipho sabo, layo yonke iminikelo yokuzunguzwa yabantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + Eks. 29.27,28. Levi 7.30,34.\x*; ngikuphe wena lamadodana akho lamadodakazi akho, ngesimiso esilaphakade\x + Levi 10.14. Dute. 18.3.\x*. Wonke ohlambulukileyo endlini yakho uzakudla\x + Levi 22.2,3,11-13.\x*.
\v 12 Ikhethelo lonke lamafutha, lekhethelo lonke lewayini elitsha, lelamabele\x + Dute. 18.4.\x*, lengqabutho yalezo abazazinikela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, ngiziphe wena\x + Eks. 23.19. Neh. 10.35,36.\x*.
\v 13 Izithelo zokuqala zakho konke okuselizweni labo abazakuletha eN\nd kosi\nd*ni kuzakuba ngokwakho\x + Eks. 34.26. Levi 2.14. Dute. 26.2.\x*. Wonke ohlambulukileyo endlini yakho uzakudla\x + 18.11.\x*.
\v 14 Konke okwehlukanisiweyo koIsrayeli kuzakuba ngokwakho\x + Levi 27.28.\x*.
\v 15 Konke okuvula isizalo, kwayo yonke inyama abakuletha eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, phakathi kwabantu laphakathi kwezifuyo, kuzakuba ngokwakho\x + Eks. 13.2.\x*; kodwa izibulo lomuntu uzalihlenga lokulihlenga, lezibulo lenyamazana engcolileyo uzalihlenga\x + Eks. 13.13; 34.20.\x*.
\v 16 Lalezo ezizahlengwa uzazihlenga kusukela sezilenyanga, njengesilinganiso sakho\x + Levi 27.2,6; Nani 3.47.\x*, ngemali \w yamashekeli\w** amahlanu, ngokweshekeli lendlu engcwele\x + Levi 27.2,6. Nani 3.47.\x*, \w elingamagera\w** angamatshumi amabili\x + Eks. 30.13.\x*.
\v 17 Kodwa izibulo lenkomo, kumbe izibulo lemvu, kumbe izibulo lembuzi, awuyikuwahlenga, angcwele\x + Dute. 15.19.\x*. Uzafafaza igazi lawo phezu kwelathi, utshise amahwahwa awo, abe ngumnikelo owenziwe ngomlilo, kube luqhatshi olumnandi eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + Levi 3.2,5.\x*.
\v 18 Lenyama yawo izakuba ngeyakho, njengesifuba esizunguziweyo lanjengomlenze wokunene, kuzakuba ngokwakho\x + Eks. 29.26,28. Levi 7.31,32,34.\x*.
\v 19 Yonke iminikelo yokuphakanyiswa yezinto ezingcwele abantwana bakoIsrayeli abayinikela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni ngiyinike wena lamadodana akho lamadodakazi akho kanye lawe, ngesimiso esilaphakade\x + 18.11.\x*. Kuyisivumelwano setswayi esilaphakade phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* kuwe lakunzalo yakho kanye lawe\x + 2 Lan. 13.5. Levi 2.13.\x*.
\p
\v 20 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuAroni: Kawuyikudla ilifa elizweni labo, kawuyikuba lesabelo phakathi kwabo; ngiyisabelo sakho lelifa lakho phakathi kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + 18.23,24. Dute. 10.9; 12.12; 14.27,29; 18.1,2. Josh. 13.14,33; 14.3; 18.7. Hez. 44.28.\x*.
\v 21 Khangela-ke, nginike abantwana bakoLevi konke okwetshumi koIsrayeli kube yilifa, ngomsebenzi wabo abawenzayo\x + 18.24,26. Levi 27.30,32. Neh. 10.37; 12.44. Heb. 7.5,8,9. Gen. 14.20; 28.22.\x*, inkonzo yethente lenhlangano\x + 3.7,8.\x*.
\v 22 Njalo abantwana bakoIsrayeli bangabe besasondela ethenteni lenhlangano\x + 17.13.\x* hlezi bathwale isono bafe\x + Levi 22.9.\x*.
\v 23 Kodwa amaLevi azakwenza inkonzo yethente lenhlangano\x + 3.7.\x*, wona athwale ububi bawo. Kuzakuba yisimiso esilaphakade ezizukulwaneni zenu; laphakathi kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli kawayikuzuza ilifa\x + 18.1. Eks. 28.38.\x*.
\v 24 Ngoba okwetshumi kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli abakunikela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni kube ngumnikelo wokuphakanyiswa, ngikunike amaLevi kube yilifa\x + 18.19,26,29.\x*. Ngakho ngitshilo kiwo \add ukuthi\add* phakathi kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli kawayikuzuza ilifa\x + 18.20,21,26.\x*.
\p
\v 25 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 26 Futhi uzakhuluma kumaLevi uthi kuwo: Nxa lithatha ebantwaneni bakoIsrayeli okwetshumi engilinike khona, kuvela kubo kube yilifa lenu, lizanikela kokwakho umnikelo wokuphakanyiswa weN\nd kosi\nd*, kube ngokwetshumi kwalokho okwetshumi\x + Neh. 10.38.\x*.
\v 27 Lomnikelo wenu wokuphakanyiswa uzabalelwa lina, njengamabele ebala lokubhulela lanjengokugcwala kwesikhamelo sewayini\x + 18.30.\x*.
\v 28 Ngalokhu lani lizanikela umnikelo wokuphakanyiswa weN\nd kosi\nd* kukho konke okwetshumi kwenu elikwemukelayo ebantwaneni bakoIsrayeli; lizanika kokwayo umnikelo wokuphakanyiswa weN\nd kosi\nd*, kuAroni umpristi.
\v 29 Kuzo zonke izipho zenu lizanikela wonke umnikelo wokuphakanyiswa weN\nd kosi\nd*; ekhethelweni lonke lazo, ingxenye yayo engcwelisiweyo evela kuyo.
\v 30 Futhi uzakuthi kuwo: Lapho linikela ikhethelo lazo elivela kuzo, kuzabalelwa amaLevi njengesivuno sebala lokubhulela lanjengesivuno sesikhamelo sewayini\x + 18.27.\x*.
\v 31 Lizakudla lokho endaweni zonke, lina lendlu yenu, ngoba kungumvuzo wenu ngomsebenzi wenu ethenteni lenhlangano\x + Mat. 10.10. Luka 10.7. 1 Kor. 9.4-14. 1 Tim. 5.17,18.\x*.
\v 32 Njalo kaliyikuthwala isono ngenxa yakho, lapho seliphakamisile ikhethelo lakho kukho\x + Levi 19.8; 22.16.\x*; kaliyikungcolisa izinto ezingcwele zabantwana bakoIsrayeli, ukuze lingafi\x + Levi 22.2,15.\x*.